                    </placeName> in <placeName type="place" key="Enge (Zürich)">Enge</placeName> <lb xml:id="p2-l7"/>
          bei <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zürich</placeName>. <date when="1846-03-04">4 Merz<note type="transcript">sic!</note>. 1846</date>.</p>
